The paper also discusses the importance of deadlock-free programs, which is a concern in Software Engineering (cs.SE). The paper's focus on developing a foundational model suggests that Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) may also be a relevant sub-category. Finally, the paper's emphasis on ensuring correctness suggests that Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) may also be a relevant sub-category.
